Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,向阿波马托克斯最后的血腥进军在这里发起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here began the last bloody march toward Appomattox
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,而格兰特将军与李将军就在那里首次碰面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where General Grant met General Lee for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢的人们用鲜血铸就历史\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And brave men bled, set the course of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我很荣幸能够来到这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so honored to be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,纪念陆路战役150周年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}celebrating the 150th anniversary of the Overland Campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢郡长罗伯茨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you to County Administrator Roberts,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢所有热忱的情景重现演员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to all the dedicated re-enactors,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  还要感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,州长奥基弗组织了如此精彩的三日活动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to Governor O'Keefe for organizing such a wonderful three-day event.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,说完了吗  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh. That's all, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,说完了  短小精悍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's it. Short and sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,至少很短小\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or at least it's short.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,加夫尼的人称内战为"北方侵略战争"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In Gaffney, people called it the "War of Northern Aggression."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,个人而言  我并不以南部邦联为荣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I personally take no pride in the Confederacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,打不赢的仗就不要打\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Avoid wars you can't win,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,更不要为奴隶制这样愚蠢的原因而战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and never raise your flag for a asinine cause like slavery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-他就来    -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's on his way.   - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,人们会忘记这事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People will move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的  你说的越少  他们越会去挖掘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They won't. The less you say, the more they'll dig.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那就让他们挖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,薇拉  能让我们单独待会儿吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Willa, could you give us two seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在外面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be right outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,麦金尼斯的事发生在大学时期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}McGinnis happened in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,堕胎则是五年之后的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The abortion happened five years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没有留下任何病历\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There aren't any medical records.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没有吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}None at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们特别确保了这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We specifically made sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,护士呢  等候室的人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A nurse? Somebody in the waiting room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只有医生一个人在场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The doctor was the only one there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那他现在在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,已经是很久以前的事了  康纳  他去世了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a long time ago, Connor. He passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我都不担心  那你也不必\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if I'm not worried, you shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就算如此  性侵的事现在成为焦点了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even still, sexual assault is part of the conversation now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的文章和专栏都会提到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every article and column mentions you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们不提供素材  就无法塑造你的形象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we offer nothing, we can't shape your image.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的很清楚  我不想曝光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I made it very clear I don't want exposure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们有新东西可说的时候  我们再说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When we have something new to say, we'll say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,薇拉  参谋长联席会议那边怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Willa. Any luck with the Joint Chiefs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,主席办公室还是说他没空\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Chairman's Office still says he's unavailable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们说可以派参谋部主任过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But they did offer to send the Director of the Joint Staff,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,明天上午11点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}11:00 a.m. tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,定下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Confirm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去白宫西楼弗兰西斯的办公室见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll meet in Francis' office at the West Wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,还有别的事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没了  我该出发了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I should get going, hit the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  康纳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Connor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,接通布鲁克斯议员的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get Congresswoman Brooks on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看看第一夫人今天下午是否有空\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And see if the First Lady will be available this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要给中国所有参加峰会的人做简报吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want a brief on everyone on the Chinese side of the Summit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不  杜兰特在华盛顿做的只是表面功夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. What Durant's doing in Washington is just the facade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是真正的谈判\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the real negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,把你手上关于冯的资料都给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me what you have on Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,冯山德  家族在共产党内很有影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Xander Feng. Deep family connections to the Party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他祖父曾跟毛泽东肩并肩作战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Grandfather fought side by side with Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在电信业势力很大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Big in the telecom industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,净资产估计有五百亿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Estimated net worth is over 50 billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:06:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,比雷蒙德还有钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More than Raymond's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,多几十亿  但谁在乎呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By a few billion. But who's counting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,除了稀土金属精炼厂之外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do they have any other business partnerships
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还有其他商业合作吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}other than the Rare Earth Refinery?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not that I could find.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  向杜兰特询问一下进度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Get a progress update from Durant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉她我们一得知冯的要求就通知她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell her I'll be in touch as soon as we know what Feng wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德·塔斯克这样的人涉足外交事务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When a man like Raymond Tusk gets involved in state diplomacy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,绝不是为了获得诺贝尔和平奖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you can be sure he's not after the Nobel Peace Prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个机会主义者  但我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's an opportunist. But so am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也许这是我的机会  能让他放松对总统的控制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe this is my opportunity to loosen his grip on the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统先生  你什么时候回华盛顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President, when are you returning to Washington?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统先生  你是否...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备在斯波特瑟尔韦尼亚待多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}do you have any idea how long you'll be in Spotsylvania?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,对于跟中国的谈判有什么看法吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any comments on the talks with the Chinese?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,能否就即将到来的峰会谈判发表一下看法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can we get a comment on the upcoming Summit talks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统今天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vice President will be working
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,将在自己的房间里办公\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from his room for the remainder of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有消息再通知你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  你什么时候回华盛顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, when are you returning to Washington?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,冯先生  很高兴见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Feng. It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,彼此彼此  副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Likewise, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,喝咖啡还是喝茶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Coffee? Tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有人问过了  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've already been offered, but thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  密查姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,从北京飞过来时间很长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a long flight from Beijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定累坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must be exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直按西方时间作息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I keep Western hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,和你们没有时差\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My midnight is your midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经看过计划书了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, have you had a chance to look over the proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,看了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,第四页\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Page four.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,精炼厂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The refinery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,与塔斯克先生合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With Mr. Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,与竞标价最高的人合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With the highest bidder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们准备与克雷顿-维斯特签订一份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're prepared to offer Clayton West
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,梅梅稀土金属精炼厂的40年租约\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a 40-year lease on the Mei Mei Rare Earth Elements Refinery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,租约上会有我的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To which I will lend my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你和雷蒙德是生意伙伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand that you and Raymond are business associates,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但你还是得公开招标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you're gonna have to open it up to bidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,塔斯克先生出价肯定比其他人高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Tusk will outbid any competitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管如此  过场还是得走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, even so, you know, for appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  过场  如果你坚持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. Appearances. If you must.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那这里就没问题了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, there are no issues here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们继续吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We may proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,第六页\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Page six.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大桥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,财政部外资投资管理委员会将批准\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Committee on Foreign Investment will approve
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一项基础建设示范工程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a pilot infrastructure project
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,建设一座从杰斐逊港到米尔福德市\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to build a bridge over the Long Island Sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,横跨长岛海峡的大桥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from Port Jefferson to Milford,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,以25年的过桥收费权作为交换\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in exchange for a 25-year toll-taking contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们考虑大桥前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Before we consider the bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我想先讨论另一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's one more item I'd like to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"考虑"  我以为大桥的事已经定了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Consider"? I thought the bridge was definite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么是确定的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing is definite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这座大桥是首要任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This bridge is a priority-one item.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对你们总统非常重要  我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's very important to your President. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你想讨论什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What would you like to discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在世界贸易组织\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The currency manipulation suit which
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,指控我们进行汇率操纵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you have filed against us in the World Trade Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which we are prepared to drop
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果满足其他条件就撤销指控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if all other conditions are met.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这次会面就是为了讨论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The point of this meeting is to allow us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不适合在正式场合谈论的事  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to say things that cannot be said in formal settings, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不希望你们撤诉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't want you to drop the lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,别在世贸组织退步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not back off in the WTO.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但你们在汇率操纵上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you've been fighting us
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,已经和我们斗争多年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on currency manipulation for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,自由浮动汇率是大势所趋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A free-floating currency is inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这下我有下手的空间了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now I have something I can work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么突然改变主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why the sudden change of heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,并不突然  只是我们这些有远见的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not sudden, it has taken those of us who are more forward-thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,花了很多年才说服其他同僚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}many years to convince our counterparts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那中国直接执行就得了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But China could just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你我都清楚  你们不需要世贸组织的裁定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, you know as well as I, you don't require a WTO ruling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你说的  得走过场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Appearances, as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要看起来像是受美国逼迫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's important that it looks like America forced us out,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是我们主动投降\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not that we gave in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那我需要时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'll need a little more time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,去和总统商量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that I can brief the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我会耐心等待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm here for as long as necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你要找谁商量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}However you would like to communicate,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I leave that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  冯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在加夫尼我们有自己的外交特色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In Gaffney we had our own brand of diplomacy:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一边握手言和  一边做好准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shake with your right hand, but hold a rock in your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,看看是谁困在这儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, look who got stuck with the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来这儿简直是找虐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We volunteered because we hate ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,南方前线一切顺利吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All's well on the Southern front?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没新闻就是没新闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No news is no news.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说那里还有火枪呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. I hear there's muskets out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候能给我们点猛料\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you giving us something real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正身处美丽的斯波特瑟尔韦尼亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're here in beautiful Spotsylvania, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是给成年人玩玩具枪找借口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is dress-up for grown men with toy guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来可以写上五百字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sounds like 500 words to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉杜兰特除非我们在世贸撤诉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell Durant that China won't discuss the bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,否则中国不愿意谈大桥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}unless we drop the WTO suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说他们不希望撤诉吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought you said they want to keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,冯希望  说明塔斯克希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Feng does, which means Tusk does.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们不知道北京是不是希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we don't know if Beijing does.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得冯在撒谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think Feng's lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,开放汇率会导致利率市场化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An open currency could free up interest rates,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,减小中国的通货膨胀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}reduce inflation in China.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他们两人都能受益\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'd both profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们或者我们将了北京的军\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If they're forcing Beijing's hand, or we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可能在峰会引起混乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that could throw the Summit into chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,正是  冯可能有后台支持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Exactly. Look, Feng may well have support,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但我猜常委会有分歧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but my guess is that the Standing Committee's divided.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样  我们打他们个措手不及\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Either way, we'll throw 'em off balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,凯茜一宣布  我们就放出撤诉的风声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's leak we're dropping the suit as soon as Cathy presents it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,只是诉讼吗  不漏点别的什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just the lawsuit? Nothing else in the leak?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,暗示与冯有关  但别点名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A hint of Feng, but no names.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,让消息传一阵子再说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's let this grow on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这回怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉不错  你怎么看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel good. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我看你准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,代码还得准备多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long on the code?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,只差几个漏洞了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a couple of bugs to work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我说明天或周三我就能回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told them tomorrow or Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,活儿还没完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Work's not done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是再往后推  你不觉得别人会奇怪吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I postpone again, don't you think it'll draw attention? I --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,等完事了也就没事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll be done when it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,漏洞修复了我就给你发邮件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll email you when the bugs are fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,挑一个公开的场所  约好时间给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Somewhere public, a place and time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你真想这么做吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, are you sure you wanna do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白风险多大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand the risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你自以为明白而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you think you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不是头回身陷险境了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't the first time I've been in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  在《先驱报》被纸割伤过手吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, yeah? Paper cuts at The Herald?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡威胁  我揭露了一个特区贩毒集团\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Death threats. When I exposed a drug ring in D.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我读过你写的报道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I read the articles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那根本不算什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's small time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我差点就接受司法保护了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I almost had to go into protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是联调局  不是什么街警\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the FBI. It's not a few street cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得自己反抗当局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think you're badass because
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就是个了不得的义士吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you're on some vigilante anarchy kick?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,起码我有胆子在报道上署上真实姓名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At least I have the balls to put my name on the work I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但你没面临过几百年的刑罚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've never faced a hundred years in prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你这自以为是的混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you self-righteous prick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我大多数朋友被关起来  永远出不来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most of my friends are locked up and rotting away
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为他们太多次以身犯险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'cause they poked the bear one too many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么  因为他们想揭露政府的监控项目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why? They wanted to expose government surveillance,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,棱镜项目  贪腐  滥用职权  酷刑和欺骗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the PRISM program, embezzlement, abuse, fucking torture, lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个记者有什么了不起  我们是战士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a journalist. Who gives a shit? We're fucking soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这已经是我生活的一部分了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's personal for me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我没选择了  但你还有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't have a choice, but you still do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没选择了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,消息从哪来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以说消息源与中国代表团关系密切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You could say a source close to the Chinese delegation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,给我个名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我只知道是一个中国商人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I know is that it's a Chinese businessman
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,和常委会关系非同一般  在峰会上进行秘密外交\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with ties to the Standing Committee back-channeling the Summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-他人在华盛顿吗    -我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- In Washington?   - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-在和谁接触    -这我也不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- With who?   - I don't know that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我去问贸易代表处  他们会证实吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I call the USTR's office, they'll confirm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道多少  就告诉了你多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm telling you as much as I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you telling me this at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,反正明天他们也会把消息放出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're going public with it tomorrow anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不如让你抢先发布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You might as well get the scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么挑中我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why me, specifically?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,内战重演的报道配不上你这样的记者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You deserve better than a Civil War reenactment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,别装做你突然变成圣诞老人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please don't pretend you've suddenly become Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在帮你的忙  也许你会承我的情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I give you something now, maybe you'll remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,将来有一天或许用得上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an investment in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不太喜欢卖人情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not big on favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我说了"也许"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just said "maybe."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,马上给我接贸易代表处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Connect me to the USTR's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,越过新闻秘书\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Skip the Press Secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他们说我想问世贸组织诉讼的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell them I want to talk about the WTO suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟谁联系的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who did you speak to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,康纳  他在向艾拉·萨伊德泄露消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Connor. He's talking to Ayla Sayyad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你透给他多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much did you fill him in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没说多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bare minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要是按之前说好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd be a lot more comfortable
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你亲自去说  我会放心许多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if it was you going directly, as we discussed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就牵涉不到我  你也就更安全了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This puts distance on me, which puts distance on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你今晚亲自去见冯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to meet with Feng tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-不用中间人    -明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No proxies.   - Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,古德温先生那边办得如何了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now where are we with Mr. Goodwin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,随时可以下手  判个35年或者无期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any day now. Thirty-five to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,网络恐怖主义  判刑都很重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cyber terrorism. Penalties are stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,务必做得干净利落  道格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This needs to be clean, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,一击致命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One fall of the axe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有消息告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep me informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为你的做法真是太勇敢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I just think what you did took so much bravery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在直播节目上  当着全国观众的面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To go on air like that, in front of the whole country,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,讲出你的遭遇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and say what you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这对我的确不容易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That means a lot to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我很钦佩两位的努力  为了帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I admire what you both have been doing to advocate for the –
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那些受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}well, for the victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是女性  就像你和我  不只是受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, women, like you and me. Not victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还有男人  这无关性别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Men, too. It's not gender-specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意参与进来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you consider pitching in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么参与\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有第一夫人支持  我们的表态就有力多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would send a strong message if we had the First Lady in our corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得我能帮上忙的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you think I could help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,妇女党团的领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, if the head of the Women's Caucus,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.07,0:15:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,以及白宫的第一和第二夫人加起来...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}both wives from the White House...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的组合他们没法无视\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a meeting they couldn't sweep under the rug.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,主席肯派人来  就已经是很好的兆头了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the fact that the Chairman sent anyone is promising,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们得保证他真能听到我们的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we need to make sure our message gets back to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只是  我没有过此类经历\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just...I haven't been through the same sort of experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这有什么妨碍呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, why should that prevent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我是不是有发言权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know if I have a right to speak about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你可是第一夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're the First Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你有权发表任何言论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a right to speak about anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-怀特先生    -马博利太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Mr. White?   - Mrs. Marbury.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我苏珊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这里挺偏僻的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know I'm a little off the beaten path.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,找这里困难吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you have any trouble finding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你给的指示很明确  找起来很轻松\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. The directions were great. Easy as pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,请进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我得承认  我都期待一整天了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to admit I've been looking forward to this all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到你们这么快就要宣布了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't realize you were announcing so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们收到了慷慨的捐款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've had some great luck with the endowment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我丈夫生前没受到多少嘉奖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, my husband didn't get much recognition while he was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,计划生育协会想以他来命名基金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was so thrilled when Planned Parenthood asked to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真让我激动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}name a fund after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,您肯同意  我们也很高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we're thrilled that you're open to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前打电话说有些问题要问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you called, you said you had some questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:17:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,问题挺敏感的  所以我想亲自来问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're delicate. That's why I wanted to come in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么个"敏感"法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Delicate", how?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很多人会抗议向未成年人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are a lot of people who will protest
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,提供这方面的经济资助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this sort of financial assistance to minors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得保证他们找不到诽谤我们的根据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we want to make sure they have no cause to smear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我丈夫这辈子  总有人想诋毁他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People tried to smear my husband his entire career.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他从不让这些事影响他的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He never let it affect the work he was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,您丈夫实施过任何非法流产手术吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did your husband ever perform any illegal abortions?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要您的答案  马博利太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you to answer me, Mrs. Marbury.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,您丈夫实施过任何非法流产手术吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did your husband perform any illegal abortions?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想讨论这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't discuss that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没有未上报的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing unreported?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,年轻人  你年纪不大  不会记得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Young man, you're not old enough to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但在过去  人人...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there was a time when everybody --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有涉及什么大人物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about any prominent figures
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,能被反堕胎人士拿来当靶子的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who the Anti-Choice crowd could vilify?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,马博利医生有没有为克莱尔·安德伍德做过堕胎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did Dr. Marbury perform an abortion for Claire Underwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不  他没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, he did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他做过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know for a fact that he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这是谎话  我想请你马上离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is not true, and I would like you to leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  马博利太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me, Mrs. Marbury.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我对您没说实话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I haven't been entirely honest with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫赛斯·格雷森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My name's Seth Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我不为计划生育协会工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't work for Planned Parenthood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}冯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}国内常委们推测  搞秘密外交的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}《华尔街电讯报》  美国在世贸组织撤诉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}香港出现了两篇文章
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}都提到了你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.61,0:18:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}要我联系副总统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不  让他来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Let him come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,给塔斯克先生打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get Mr. Tusk on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你真该为自己感到羞愧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should ashamed of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我是为了你好  马博利太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm doing this for your own good, Mrs. Marbury.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,想想媒体炒作的后果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Imagine the media frenzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫生前的名声尽毁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your husband's legacy, destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,媒体日日夜夜追着你不放\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The press hounding you, day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,计划生育基金  也没有了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Planned Parenthood Fund, gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么知道你是不是为她工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do I know you work for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是什么右翼狂热分子  打算摧毁...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That you're not just some right-wing fanatic who wants to destro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:19:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,否则我就不会亲自登门拜访了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I wouldn't have done you the courtesy of paying a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,来的就不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There would've been an army of satellite trucks
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,而是一队卫星转播车了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}at your door instead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会告诉任何人的  如果你是担心这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I won't tell anyone, if that's what you're worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫有没有对他帮助过的女人做过任何记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did your husband keep records of any kind of who he assisted?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,任何东西  笔记或非公开记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything at all? Notes? Unofficial records?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他有一本日记\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He kept a journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你还能找到吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you still have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看看吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我得把它带走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh. I need to take this with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能把那页撕掉吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't you just take out that page?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人找到这本日记  这几页又缺了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone finds this with pages missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那会引起怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that could raise eyebrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这里面有他60年的人生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's 60 years of his life in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,从我们相遇到他去世\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From when we met until he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那你希望那60年被遗忘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And do you want six decades
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,却只剩下25年前8月的一个晚上吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}reduced to one night in August...25 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,想象一下这里当时的情形\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now just imagine what it looked like back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.49,0:20:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,山脊边缘是茂密的灌木丛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The edge of the ridge was a dense thicket,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,北方军队得以长驱直入  在骡子鞋列队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which allowed the Northern troops to come in and form on the Mule Shoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,南方军在山脊顶端\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now the Southern regiments were entrenched
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这一带挖好了战壕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in this area at the apex of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的地形迫使双方向下走  逼近彼此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the topography really forced the two sides down towards each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就是血腥角\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the Bloody Angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨晚还读到了相关内容\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was reading about it last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,短兵相接  白刃相见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Close quarters, hand-to-hand combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,据说  南北双方共有一万五千名士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All told, about 15,000 Union-Confederate soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在血腥角这块半英里宽的战场上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}lost their lives here at the Bloody Angle,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,失去了生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on a battlefield that's only about half a mile wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统先生  我们今天为您准备了一份惊喜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, Mr. Vice President, we have a surprise for you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,向您介绍麦高文旅第12军团的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to introduce you to Corporal Augustus Elijah Underwood
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,奥古斯都·以利亚·安德伍德下士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the 12th Regiment of the McGowan Brigade,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,您的曾曾曾祖父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your great-great-great-grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这场战役中牺牲于此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I died here in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:20:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得是搞错了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think there's been a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:21:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我祖父从没说过祖上有人参加过内战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My grandfather never mentioned any Underwoods in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做过调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We did our research.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是在这里战斗牺牲的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He definitely fought and died here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有24岁  而我儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was 24. And my son,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你的曾曾祖父只有两岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your great-great-grandfather was two years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没见过他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就是在这里吗  在血腥角\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It happened here, at the Bloody Angle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在那片林子边上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At the edge of those woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我的脑袋被石头砸扁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My skull was bashed in with a rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,奥古斯都  谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Augustus, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这边  还有一些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, uh, over here we've got something that's,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}uh, very interesting as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, j—just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.33,0:21:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,接着说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,当时正是半夜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的子弹打光了  只剩下刺刀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we were out of musket balls, just bayonets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,而且只有一半人有刺刀  我什么都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only half of us had those. I had nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,只有赤手空拳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just these hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,天很黑  什么都看不见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So dark, couldn't see nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但能听北方佬在朝我们跑来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you could hear 'em, the Yanks, runnin' toward us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,接着就能闻到他们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then you could smell 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我遇到的第一个北方佬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First Yank that brushed up against me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,被我掐住了脖子  倒在地上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I grab him by the throat, fall down on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我用力打他  打到皮开肉绽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I bit him so hard, I could taste the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他抓起一块石头  砸中了这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then he grabs a rock and brings it down right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.77,0:22:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我就这么死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that was that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.43,0:22:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我被埋在万人冢里  没有墓碑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was buried in a mass grave, no headstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.03,0:22:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,能给您和奥古斯都拍张合影吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could we get a picture with you and Augustus?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.40,0:22:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.53,0:22:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他相当认真啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He takes it rather seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.22,0:22:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  他们都很认真\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, yeah. They all do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.48,0:22:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,前面有我们重建的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, up ahead, we have examples of,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.59,0:22:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,邦联军壁垒的模型\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}uh, Confederate ramparts that we've reconstructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.34,0:22:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,可以看到他们是如何伐木挖战壕的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you can see how they cut the timber and made the trenches.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在战斗过程中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now these trenches traded hands many times
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.43,0:22:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这些战壕几次易手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}over the course of the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.91,0:22:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你有钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你归我们管  没错  我们有钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We own you. Yes, we have keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我去把衣服穿上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna put some clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.44,0:22:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,别想衣服的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forget your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.52,0:22:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你的原话"你真想这么做吗"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I quote, "You sure you wanna do this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"我没选择了  但你还有"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I quote, "I don't have a choice, but you do."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.46,0:22:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈以为自己在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the fuck do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:22:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他应该知道他究竟要做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He should know what he's getting into.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是丝绸睡裤吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are those silk pajamas?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,近距离看更有档次了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks even fancier in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.44,0:23:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,腰果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cashew.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.19,0:23:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不  别碰她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Don't touch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.68,0:23:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,过来  小家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, there, little guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.82,0:23:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前在监控里见过你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen you before on camera, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,请把她放下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please put her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不要冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't take the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.43,0:23:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这这双鞋是在彭尼百货公司买的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I bought these shoes at J.C. Penney,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,含税价72块\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}$72 with tax.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.99,0:23:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,橡胶鞋底  用水就能冲干净\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rubber soles. You can clean 'em off with a hose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.89,0:23:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你  你弄伤她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, you're hurting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.60,0:23:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有一只宠物  他叫嘉文·奥尔西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have a pet, too. His name is Gavin Orsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.05,0:23:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我说"坐下"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said, "Sit."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧你多乖呀  嘉文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look what a good boy you are, Gavin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.25,0:24:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我这么做吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that what you need me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.46,0:24:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,安静  我说"去捡"  你就去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quiet. When I say "fetch," you fetch.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.30,0:24:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们去抓卢卡斯  就像我们说好的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now we are going to fetch Lucas, just like we discussed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.62,0:24:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是敢咬我  我就杀了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you try to bite my hand, I will put you to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.22,0:24:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,介意我拿两瓶吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mind if I take a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.40,0:24:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,道格·斯坦普  我是副总统的幕僚长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doug Stamper, I'm the Vice President's Chief of Staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.91,0:25:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  坐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.08,0:25:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我祖父参加过革命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My grandfather fought in the Revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.17,0:25:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,中国当时很穷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}China was poor, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.71,0:25:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很难买到糖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sugar was hard to come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.03,0:25:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,现在中国到处能买到糖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now sugar's everywhere in China.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.29,0:25:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要来杯古典鸡尾酒吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you like Old-Fashioneds?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.21,0:25:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.58,0:25:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到新闻了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.59,0:25:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你们政府对我们撤诉非常高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your government was enthusiastic about our dropping the suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.67,0:25:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还在国内将其鼓吹为一场胜利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They've touted it as a victory back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.91,0:25:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,确实是胜利  但不是我们想要的胜利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is a victory, but not the victory we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.39,0:25:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我们很难相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're finding that difficult to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.32,0:25:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我们  是指副总统吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By "we," you mean the Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.34,0:25:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我指的是美国政府\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean the American government.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.82,0:25:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他声称自己就代表美国政府\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which he proclaims to represent.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.30,0:25:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  而我代表他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He does. And I'm representing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.61,0:25:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,斯坦普先生  别吹嘘你的地位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't inflate your status, Mr. Stamper.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.84,0:25:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你不过是个跑腿的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're nothing but an errand boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.41,0:25:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你要对副总统说什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you have a message for the Vice President?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.72,0:25:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他代表美国政府\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he represents the American government,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.16,0:25:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那他为什么没能传达我的要求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then why did he fail to communicate my request?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.71,0:25:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们质疑你的合法性  冯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We question your legitimacy, Mr. Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.92,0:25:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你们代表团的做法和言论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing your delegation has done or said has,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.84,0:26:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,都与你的要求背道而驰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in any way, supported your requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.76,0:26:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,闻闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Smell that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.60,0:26:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我用了高档珍稀的麦卡伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I use Macallan Rare and Fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.98,0:26:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,1926年产  一瓶四万美金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}1926. $40,000 a bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.48,0:26:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前酗酒  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You used to be an alcoholic, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.66,0:26:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,  只能克制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not "used to be." Still am. A sober one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.74,0:26:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你怀念这味道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you miss it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.91,0:26:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是五千美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Five thousand dollars you just spilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.61,0:26:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我会寄张支票给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll send you a check.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.97,0:26:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你  斯坦普先生  即便你只是个跑腿的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like you, Mr. Stamper, even if you're just an errand boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.04,0:26:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我再问你一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.06,0:26:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你要对副总统说什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is your message for the Vice President?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.66,0:26:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,恢复起诉  否则杰斐逊港大桥项目将取消\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There will be no Port Jefferson Bridge unless the lawsuit is reintroduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.55,0:26:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,到时  常委会会有人抗议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you do, there will be those on the Standing Committee who protest,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.92,0:26:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我会搞定他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'll manage them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.01,0:26:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大多数人想要改革\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The majority want reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.80,0:26:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我会告诉副总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll tell the Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.48,0:26:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,斯坦普先生  还有一条\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Stamper, one more message.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.44,0:26:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,请提醒副总统  我们来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please remind the Vice President that we are both here at
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.61,0:27:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是应我们共同的朋友塔斯克先生的邀请\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the behest of our mutual friend, Mr. Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.23,0:27:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,如果副总统不愿意合作  我就直接跳过他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the Vice President fails to cooperate, I will simply bypass him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.74,0:27:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.16,0:27:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是道格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.29,0:27:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.57,0:27:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,跟冯谈了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Spoke with Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.60,0:27:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,给你的洋葱圈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here's your onion rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.24,0:27:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道朗斯特里特将军就是在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you know that General Longstreet was shot here,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.60,0:27:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,被他自己人意外误伤害死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}accidentally, by his own men in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.91,0:27:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No...I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.18,0:27:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  跟我介绍一下进展吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Bring me up to date.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.94,0:27:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,跟冯谈得怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are we with Feng?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.93,0:27:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他要我们恢复诉讼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wants us to resume the lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.31,0:27:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,看来他要坚持立场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, he's sticking to his guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.27,0:27:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不起诉  大桥项目就取消\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we don't reintroduce it, there's no bridge project.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.88,0:27:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那样总统会很失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that would greatly upset the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.11,0:27:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要我转达冯的意思吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you want me to deliver Feng's message?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.04,0:27:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.64,0:27:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就要让总统生气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want the President angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.73,0:28:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不过要想办法不让他怪罪在我身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The tricky part is making sure he doesn't direct it toward me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.31,0:28:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那你要我做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.21,0:28:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,联系凯茜的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get a hold of Cathy's people.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.37,0:28:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,决不能提及诉讼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not mention the lawsuit at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.88,0:28:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们自己提大桥项目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have them bring up the bridge instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.27,0:28:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,看看冯是不是在虚张声势\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's see if Feng is bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.34,0:28:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.46,0:28:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,得吸取朗斯特里特的教训  他树大招风\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must learn from Longstreet. He rode too high in the saddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.18,0:28:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果明天有人朝我开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If a bullet comes my way tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.76,0:28:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那绝不会是意外  而且我得赶快躲开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it will not be an accident, and I must be quick to duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.29,0:28:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们  感谢你们的到来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gentlemen, thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.38,0:28:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统会出席吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is the Vice President attending?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.37,0:28:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不会  他不在华盛顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, he's not. He's out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.18,0:28:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是决定用他的办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just decided to use his office
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.15,0:28:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他的比我的大得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because it's a bit bigger than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.09,0:28:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.45,0:28:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这不是你们第一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know this isn't the first conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.21,0:28:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,谈性侵犯的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you've had about sexual assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.76,0:28:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们和议员女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've had a very open dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.12,0:28:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,已经进行了一段时间的公开对话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with the Congresswoman for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.20,0:28:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可以说"公开"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Open" is one way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.29,0:28:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒觉得参谋长联席会议只是在默默忍受我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think the Joint Chiefs have tolerated my concerns, but
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.78,0:28:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,公平来讲  我们一直有做出积极回应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To be fair, we've been quite responsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.78,0:29:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,过去两年里...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over the past two years alone, we --
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.65,0:29:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,议员女士对我表达了她的沮丧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Congresswoman has expressed her frustration to me
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.97,0:29:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这件事上仍有改进空间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that there's still room for improvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.34,0:29:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,安德伍德夫人  我能说几句吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Underwood, if I may.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.70,0:29:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,请讲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.52,0:29:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事我们十分看重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is an issue we've grappled with seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.24,0:29:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们增加了相关教育和防范措施\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Increased education and prevention measures,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.57,0:29:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,改整汇报流程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}restructuring the reporting process,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.78,0:29:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,杜绝军事法庭的滥用职权现象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}insulating courts martial from abuse of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.35,0:29:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但还是不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's still not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.73,0:29:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会进行民事审判的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Civilian jurisdiction is not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.25,0:29:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都清楚这是议员女士所希望的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're all aware that's what the Congresswoman would prefer,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.93,0:29:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们不会允许我们...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we won't allow our cha--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.63,0:29:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我迟到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Am I late?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.25,0:29:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的错  会面提前了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's my fault. The meeting got pushed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.04,0:29:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我本想给你发邮件的  非常抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I meant to email you. I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.92,0:29:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  请坐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's fine. Please, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.90,0:29:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不知道您也会来  沃克夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We didn't know you'd be attending, Mrs. Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.41,0:29:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉打断你们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry for interrupting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.49,0:29:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,请继续\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.26,0:29:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,正如我刚刚所说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As I was saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.86,0:29:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,将性侵案件的审判权完全交给民事法庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}putting sexual assault cases entirely in the hands of civilian courts
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.37,0:29:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,从根本上侵蚀了军队自我约束的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}fundamentally erodes the military's ability to self-discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.74,0:30:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那要是实施民事监管  而不是民事法庭呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about civilian oversight instead of civilian courts?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.09,0:30:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,任何让步  都会一发不可收拾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a slippery slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.61,0:30:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对于种族融合  也曾有人说过类似的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There were those who said the same about racial integration.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.89,0:30:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,融合没有改变核心的运作本质...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Integration didn't change the core operational nature of the --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.70,0:30:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但的确证明了军方可以实现自我改革\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it did prove that the military could shape its own evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.89,0:30:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那是没错  但就这个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Absolutely. But in this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.31,0:30:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,民事监管不是解决办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}civilian oversight is not the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.58,0:30:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我丈夫没有军衔  但他监管军方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My husband is a civilian who oversees the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.60,0:30:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道想说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you suggesting that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.79,0:30:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,民众在这种问题上无从提供指导吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}civilians can offer no guidance in matters like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.69,0:30:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  沃克夫人  我完全不是那个意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me, Mrs. Walker. I didn't mean to suggest that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.24,0:30:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那或许你该听听你对面的民众是怎么想的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then maybe you should listen to the civilian sitting across from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.76,0:30:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.96,0:30:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你们出版的性侵防范读物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is from your own sexual assault prevention literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.88,0:30:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,书里写道  有些情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in it, it says in some cases
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.37,0:30:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,更应该屈从  而不是抵抗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it may be advisable to submit than to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.18,0:30:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想  这方面显然还有可以改进的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it's quite clear that there's still room for improvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.57,0:30:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道冯山德吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you know about Xander Feng?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.10,0:31:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在新闻上看到才知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not 'til I saw his name on {\u1}the wire{\u0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.10,0:31:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs16\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}美联社  路透社等大新闻通讯社发布的新闻  媒体获得后会进行转载
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.83,0:31:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他曾两次被指控腐败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's been charged with corruption twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.58,0:31:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,两次指控都撤销了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Both times the charges were dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.97,0:31:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道在中国获罪后会怎样吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know what happens in China if you're convicted?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.81,0:31:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-我猜不会有好事    -判死刑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm guessing it's not good.   - You die.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.14,0:31:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我说对了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.87,0:31:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这人如果再上"过场法庭"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're talking about a man who's only one {\u1}kangaroo court{\u0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.87,0:31:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}指全是摆摆样子的法庭  根本不会认真按照法律进行审判
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.87,0:31:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就必死无疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}away from lethal injection,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.55,0:31:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他富可敌国  腐败昭然若揭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who's filthy rich and clearly corrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.47,0:31:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,中方就派这样的人来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this is who the Chinese send?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.20,0:31:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你问错人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're asking the wrong guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.73,0:31:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别再躲躲闪闪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop dodging.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.80,0:31:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不过是传了个话  仅此而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I passed a note in class. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.08,0:31:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们信任你  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We placed our faith in you, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.19,0:31:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有今明两天时间  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We still have the rest of the day and all of tomorrow, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.55,0:31:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要这座桥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need this bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.53,0:31:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,否则我的基建项目就得叫停\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Otherwise, we have to stall my infrastructure program.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.89,0:31:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没有外国投资  没法削减赤字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No foreign investment, no deficit reduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.30,0:31:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,中方知道这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the Chinese know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.29,0:31:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就是拿这个做筹码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're using it for leverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.42,0:31:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是为了什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.41,0:31:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that I'm not sure of.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.92,0:31:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们派你去斯波特瑟尔韦尼亚干什么  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then why did we send you to Spotsylvania, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.77,0:31:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这些问题你该心里有数的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're supposed to have answers to these questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.73,0:31:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生  我一小时前和冯先生联系过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, I spoke to Mr. Feng an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.94,0:31:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What'd he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.49,0:31:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,子弹来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here comes the bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.35,0:31:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他说弗兰克没表达清楚他的意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He claims that Frank hasn't been delivering his messages properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.32,0:31:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经逐字复述了他的要求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have conveyed his requests word for word.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.07,0:32:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他说  你一直在唱反调\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He says you've been doing the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.03,0:32:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟是谁在负责私下沟通  我还是雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whose responsible for the back-channeling here, me or Raymond?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.35,0:32:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.49,0:32:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是来帮忙的  不是来谈判的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm simply here to facilitate, not negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.98,0:32:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可你还继续私下联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yet you continue to have private conversations with
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.08,0:32:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,北京所谓的密使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beijing's supposed emissary.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.96,0:32:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, Frank --
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.84,0:32:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你要信任冯先生  而不是我吗  雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you prepared to trust Mr. Feng's word over mine, Raymond?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.81,0:32:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没人质疑你的话  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one is doubting your word, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.42,0:32:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如果冯真的是为了他政府的利益\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, if Feng is truly representing his government's interest,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.90,0:32:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么他在我这儿一套  雷蒙德那儿一套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then why is he telling Raymond one thing and telling me another?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.52,0:32:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那大桥项目取消是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you explain the bridge falling through?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.57,0:32:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,自由浮动货币能让他受益\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, he personally profits from a free-floating currency,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.62,0:32:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,和他合作的人都是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just as anyone would who's in business with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.94,0:32:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就比如你  雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}such as yourself, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.40,0:32:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,精炼厂和大桥是两码事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The refinery and the bridge are two completely different issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.28,0:32:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们先说桥的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's keep our focus, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.94,0:32:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,必须重谈建桥的事  没得商量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want the bridge back on the table, end of story.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.55,0:32:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-凯瑟琳    -我明早第一个提这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Catherine?   - It'll be the first item I bring up in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.04,0:32:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克  先按兵不动  别联系冯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Frank, stay put for now. But don't contact Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.45,0:32:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是  雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that goes for you, too, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.77,0:32:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,建桥的事谈妥之前不许你们再私下会面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want any more back-channeling until the bridge is revived.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.88,0:32:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳  有什么事直接和我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, Catherine, you communicate directly with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.10,0:32:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.91,0:32:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那就先说到这里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. We're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.42,0:32:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,第一滴血溅了出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The first drops of blood have been spilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.66,0:32:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,子弹擦过我的脸颊  但我没有倒下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bullet grazed my cheek, but I haven't fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.95,0:33:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,道格  想个办法让我见到冯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doug, find me a way to meet Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.30,0:33:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有件事我们得先谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to discuss something first.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.11,0:33:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.08,0:33:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚跟一个叫赛斯·格雷森的人通了电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just got off the phone with a guy named Seth Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.66,0:33:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我和我丈夫聊过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've spoken with my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.50,0:33:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,道格说了  感谢你能见我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doug told me. Thank you for fitting me in today.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.20,0:33:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-是这个吧    -86年8月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Is that it?   - August '86.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.89,0:33:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们凭什么相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And why should we trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.49,0:33:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,有些证据康纳没能抹去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was evidence that Connor didn't make disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.19,0:33:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我本可以把这个拿给《美国周刊》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could've taken this to Us Weekly
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.02,0:33:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,报酬够我买新房了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and bought a new house.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.48,0:33:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可我把它带来给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Instead, I brought it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.91,0:33:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时面试的时候你为什么没申请\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And why didn't you apply when I was interviewing candidates?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.10,0:33:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,申请了也没用  薇拉不喜欢我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no point. Willa doesn't like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.88,0:33:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,她怕我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I intimidate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.18,0:33:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这日记就是我的简历\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That journal is my version of a resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.95,0:33:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,或是勒索信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or extortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.59,0:33:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我没想勒索你  安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not extorting you, Mrs. Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.94,0:33:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想强调\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just highlighting the difference
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.83,0:33:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好的决定和正确决定的差别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}between a good choice and the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.29,0:33:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那你说解雇刚聘用三个月的媒体主管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And tell me, how would we handle the repercussions
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.78,0:33:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所带来的影响我们要怎么应对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of firing our comm director three months after we hire him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.83,0:34:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用解雇他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't fire him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.62,0:34:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉他雇用我是为了减轻工作量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You tell him that you're bringing me on board to help with the workload.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.47,0:34:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他还负责你  我负责你丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He stays on with you. I cover your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.30,0:34:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,康纳不会喜欢和我合作的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Connor will hate working with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.49,0:34:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,过几个月我再找人来挖他墙角\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll arrange a job offer elsewhere in a few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.39,0:34:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,到那时  他会愿意接受的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By the time it comes in, he'll want to move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.07,0:34:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,康纳也知道  如何保证他不会公开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Connor knows. What's to prevent him from going public?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.82,0:34:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我能搞定康纳·埃利斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can handle Connor Ellis.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.37,0:34:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你只能相信我  我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You just have to take me on my word on that. I –
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.97,0:34:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我只知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here's what I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.54,0:34:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你要弄垮我比我扳倒你容易得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is far easier for you to destroy me than the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.22,0:34:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我得和我丈夫谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to speak to my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.75,0:34:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.82,0:34:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有复印\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't make any copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.41,0:34:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你手上的是唯一的一份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.93,0:35:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,纯尊尼获加黑牌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, Johnny Walker Black, neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.71,0:35:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-东西在哪    -我口袋里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where is it?   - It's in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.65,0:35:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,给我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.04,0:35:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-有问题吗    -没有  一切就绪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Something up?   - No. We're good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.75,0:35:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来很紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You seem nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.34,0:35:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我干了20年违法乱纪的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just because I've been breaking the law for 20 years
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.27,0:35:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是会觉得紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}doesn't mean I don't still get nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.97,0:35:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-嘉文    -别说我的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Gavin.   - Do not say my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.06,0:35:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.27,0:35:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题的  我们练习过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's gonna be fine. We practiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.09,0:35:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我有信心  会成功的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm confident. This is gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.47,0:36:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我请你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got your drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.32,0:36:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他非常有资历\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's more than qualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.62,0:36:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你的直觉怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do your instincts tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.01,0:36:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想再增加曝光度了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That I just don't wanna end up more exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.66,0:36:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,格雷森都知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, Grayson already knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.19,0:36:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要是不表现出...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, if we don't exhibit some degree of --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.88,0:36:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,让道格去查查他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have Doug look into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.51,0:36:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我们有没有筹码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's see if there's some leverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.41,0:36:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们不知道他能查到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but we don't know what he'll find
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.69,0:36:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候能查到  这期间他会做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or when,  or what he'll do in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.97,0:36:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这会让我们无从防备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that puts us into unchartered territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.25,0:36:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们解雇康纳  他也会告密的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, Connor will expose us, too, if we let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.84,0:36:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,处理得好就不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not if it goes smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.44,0:36:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果现在拒绝格雷森  我们无法预料后果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we turn away Grayson now, we can't predict anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.14,0:36:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他比我们可要输得起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, look, he has a lot less to lose than we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.81,0:37:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我只是不相信他  弗兰西斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. I just – I don't think we can trust him, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.96,0:37:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,如果康纳尽了职我们也不会有这麻烦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We wouldn't be having this conversation if Connor had done his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.78,0:37:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我宁可要个不可信任的手下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'd rather manage someone I don't trust
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.46,0:37:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,也不要做事不周到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than someone who is reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.45,0:37:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  下一步怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine. What's the next step?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.09,0:37:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我先亲自跟格雷森谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to talk to Grayson myself first,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.09,0:37:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我让道格跟康纳谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then I'll have Doug talk to Connor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.43,0:37:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你那边怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.05,0:37:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你关注新闻了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You been following the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.51,0:37:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,对我们来说是好是坏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it bad for us? Or good?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.21,0:37:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,都有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could go either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.56,0:37:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,需要我的话就开口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm here if you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.01,0:37:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我明天就回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.81,0:37:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-我爱你    -我也爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I love you.   - Love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.02,0:37:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-都准备好了吗    -都准备好了  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We all set?   - All set, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.27,0:37:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.90,0:37:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不  把灯关掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no, no. Turn those off.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.41,0:37:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,把灯关掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Turn those off.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.47,0:37:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.45,0:37:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这边走  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right this way, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.54,0:38:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,奥古斯都会拉小提琴吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did Augustus play?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.13,0:38:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like to think I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.53,0:38:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己的名字是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's your own name?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.55,0:38:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里的时候  我就是奥古斯都·安德伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I'm here, I'm Augustus Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.49,0:38:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你的真名是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.88,0:38:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这不真实吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doesn't this feel real to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.08,0:38:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你能带我去看他死的地方吗  具体地点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will you show me where he died? The exact spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.62,0:39:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.90,0:39:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去向我的祖先致敬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna pay respects to my ancestor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.02,0:39:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,请给我点隐私\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would appreciate a little privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.06,0:39:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这里等着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.59,0:39:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰在移动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}John on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.20,0:39:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那些树后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just beyond those trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.39,0:39:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  我自己过去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you. I'll be good from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.57,0:39:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.19,0:39:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你没等太久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope you haven't waited long.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.44,0:39:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很平静  我不介意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's peaceful here. I didn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.13,0:39:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,现在很平静  但有一万五千人曾在这里丧生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peaceful now. Fifteen thousand men died in these woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.57,0:40:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我的曾曾曾祖父死在我们站的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My grandfather's grandfather died where we're standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.04,0:40:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我的祖父在革命中牺牲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My grandfather was killed in the Revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.16,0:40:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.13,0:40:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你怕死吗  副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you fear death, Mr. Vice President?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.26,0:40:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,跟其他人一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No more or less than any man.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.80,0:40:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡给我激励  让我去经历一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It motivates me. To experience everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.46,0:40:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在一切化为粪土之前  努力成就伟业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}accomplish all I can before it all vanishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.57,0:40:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在这方面我觉得我们很像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you and I are similar in that regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.26,0:40:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们为什么要彼此背道而驰呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then why are we working at cross purposes?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.02,0:40:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now what you mean is,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.04,0:40:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"为什么我不服从你和塔斯克先生"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Why am I not submitting to you and Mr. Tusk?"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.71,0:40:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你在破坏谈判\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're sabotaging the negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.40,0:40:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,而你在利用谈判达到自己的目的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you're using them for your own personal ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.42,0:40:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,错了  我花了七年时间说服常委\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wrong. It's taken me seven years to convince the Standing Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.80,0:40:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是应该采取的做法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that this was the right course of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.38,0:40:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可以给你和塔斯克带来数十亿收益的做法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A course of action that will earn you and Tusk billions.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.11,0:40:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你约我在这里见面就为了攻击我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did you want this meeting? Just to attack me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.20,0:40:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,为了给雷蒙德带个信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To send a message to Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.52,0:40:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,美国总统和我不是他的傀儡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The President of the United States and I are not his puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.51,0:40:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你就这么跟他说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now you tell him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.07,0:40:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好  桥的事没戏了  没有挽回余地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine. The bridge deal is dead. There will be no saving it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.64,0:40:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,随你怎么折腾吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stick a knife through its heart and put an apple in its mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.71,0:41:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不在乎呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't shed a tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.16,0:41:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你们总统会把失败归咎于你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your President will ascribe the failure to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.46,0:41:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意冒这个险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll take the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.72,0:41:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好好想想  副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think strategically, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.45,0:41:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是把我们往绝路上推\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're setting us on a very dangerous course.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.84,0:41:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道格兰特将军是如何击败李将军的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know how Grant defeated Lee?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.76,0:41:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他的人更多  仅此而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He had more men. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.66,0:41:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他愿意让他们去送死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he was willing to let them die.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.41,0:41:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是屠杀  而非策略  赢得了战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was butchery, not strategy, which won the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.47,0:41:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,塔斯克先生和我有丰厚资源可以利用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Tusk and I have great resources at our disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.56,0:41:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,把你们的钱加起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Add up all your billions together,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.85,0:41:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,相当于斯洛伐克的国内生产总值\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you get the GDP of Slovakia.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.01,0:41:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我背后是美利坚合众国的联邦政府\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have the federal government of the United States of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.88,0:41:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的钱吓不倒我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your money doesn't intimidate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.90,0:41:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你最多能买到影响力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The most that you can buy is influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.75,0:41:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但我可以利用宪法施压\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I wield Constitutional authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.56,0:41:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,最强大的军队并不总是能取胜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The strongest army doesn't always win.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.30,0:41:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,毛主席从几千人的军队开始发迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mao started out with only a few thousand men.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.60,0:41:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他们打下了半个亚洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They took over half a continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.66,0:41:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,毛主席已经死了  他的中国也死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mao is dead. And so is his China.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.32,0:41:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但我没死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.99,0:42:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,目前还没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.73,0:42:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了  你的祖先为战败的一方而战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't forget. Your ancestor fought for the losing side.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.04,0:42:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,成者王  败者寇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is no sacred ground for the conquered.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.07,0:42:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这里有九千余台服务器  分属几百家客户\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have over 9,000 servers here, utilized by several hundred clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.75,0:42:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,从小商贩到大公司都有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything from small businesses to major corporations.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.53,0:42:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,最大的客户都有谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are some of the largest clients?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.10,0:42:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这里最大的是美国电话电报公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The largest here is AT&T.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.20,0:42:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的服务器占了这层的大半空间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their servers occupy more than half of the floor space.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.66,0:42:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,能让我看看吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And can you show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.59,0:42:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.48,0:42:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这边走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.97,0:43:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你昨晚有没有去见冯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you or did you not meet with Feng last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.48,0:43:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这话从何说起  雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is this coming from, Raymond?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.13,0:43:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Answer the question, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.95,0:43:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,上次谈话后我就没联系过他了  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have not contacted him since you and I spoke, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.02,0:43:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,完全按照你的要求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just as you instructed me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.86,0:43:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,冯可不是这么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not according to Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.26,0:43:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是也不许见他吗  雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe you were also instructed to avoid him too, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.02,0:43:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他自己找上门来的  我只是接了电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He reached out to me. I just answered the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.97,0:43:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们事先有明确的协议  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We had clear, prearranged terms, frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.02,0:43:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,私下接触了数月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Months of back-channeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.61,0:43:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我在第一线  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am on the front lines, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.37,0:43:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我的亲身体会是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I can tell you firsthand
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.86,0:43:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在面对的这个国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that we are dealing with a regime
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.25,0:43:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅有事隐瞒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that is not being forthright and
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.03,0:43:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,而且会利用任何风吹草动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will seize upon the faintest whiff of trepidation.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.22,0:43:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这是次考验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.43,0:43:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,看我们被逼到什么境地会投降\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To see how far they can push us before we break.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.09,0:43:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,别让他们得逞  中止谈判\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not play their game. End the talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.60,0:43:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能反应过度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't overreact here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.19,0:43:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他们中止了商贸联委会的谈判\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, they walked away from the Joint Commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.63,0:43:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也可以中止峰会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can walk away from the Summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.95,0:43:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,经济损失难以估量  市场会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The economic fallout would be catastrophic. The market would--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.76,0:43:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,要么向这个新兴超级大国卑躬屈膝也行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or we can just kowtow and submit to the new reigning superpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.35,0:43:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,别夸大其词  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be hyperbolic, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.03,0:43:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可是在跟全球四分之一的人打交道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we are dealing with one quarter of the world's population.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.69,0:44:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生  这会酿成大错的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, you would be making a disastrous mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.11,0:44:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底效忠谁  雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are your allegiances, Raymond?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.80,0:44:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是冯山德还是美国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With Xander Feng or to the United --?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.47,0:44:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么敢质疑我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't you dare question me about --
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.41,0:44:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,行了  安静\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.52,0:44:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我犯了两个错误\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There were two mistakes. Both of them mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.84,0:44:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,第一个错误是允许你  雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The first was allowing you, Raymond,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.90,0:44:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,让你的商业伙伴参与谈判\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to enlist your business partner for these talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.95,0:44:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was simply trying to --
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.81,0:44:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而第二个错误就是让你去  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the second was enlisting you, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.98,0:44:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不但没把话说清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Instead of clarity,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.88,0:44:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,还造成误解  外交表现糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we got miscommunication. That's poor diplomacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.97,0:44:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生  听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, listen --
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.26,0:44:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你们的话我都听过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no. I've listened. To both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.36,0:44:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但只听到了互相谴责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And all I've heard is accusations.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.15,0:44:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们谁都不愿负责  那我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now if neither of you will take responsibility, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.69,0:44:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们撤出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're pulling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.21,0:44:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,并非是听从你的意见  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not because you suggested it, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.82,0:44:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而是因为你协商失败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's because you've made such a mess of these negotiations
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.00,0:44:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,让我不得不表现出强硬态度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that I have no other choice than a show of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.37,0:44:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个都让我很失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've both disappointed me greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.46,0:44:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President --
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.75,0:44:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,总统已离线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The President has left the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.11,0:44:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德  你还在吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond, are you still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.30,0:45:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他20年来第一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the first time he's ever hung up on me
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.71,0:45:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,挂我电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.24,0:45:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为你难过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh. I feel for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.64,0:45:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,再见  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goodbye, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.08,0:45:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  杀戮开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the butchery begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.66,0:45:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,从这排起  到后面七排全是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all the way down this row and the next seven rows over.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.44,0:45:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你想进去看看  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now you wanted to see inside one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.38,0:45:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是  那就太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, that would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.44,0:45:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,进去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.06,0:45:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,其实没什么好看的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's not much to it, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.53,0:45:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一堆硬盘和电线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a lot of hard drives and wires.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.84,0:45:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,说到文件备份  如果突然停电\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So in terms of back-up, if the power goes down,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.91,0:45:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,比如碰上自然灾害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}some natural disaster hits,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.33,0:45:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,龙卷风或地震之类的  要怎么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like a storm, or an earthquake, what exactly --?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.98,0:45:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-趴在地上    -不许动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- On the ground.   - Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.07,0:45:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-不  我    -立刻趴下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, no, I      - right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.91,0:45:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下  立刻趴下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On the ground! On the ground now!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.43,0:45:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了趴下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said on the fucking ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.58,0:45:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我一起回特区吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why don't you ride back to D.C. with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.43,0:45:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有事要谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to discuss something.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.74,0:45:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.42,0:45:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们车里谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll talk about it in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.45,0:46:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,今天  我们在陆路战役游客中心破土动工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Today, we break earth on the Overland Campaign Visitors Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.91,0:46:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我们的后代\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So that generations to come
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.00,0:46:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,能深刻体会这片圣地的重要意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will fully absorb the importance of this hallowed ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.31,0:46:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,铭记这片战役打响的荒野\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the wilderness where the campaign commenced.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.58,0:46:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,奥古斯都  请你来好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Augustus. Would you do the honor?
